name: Observe
description:
A self-timer selfie when there wasn't any App control for cameras.

Anyway, the image above was taken in Morocco, where I experienced solo traveling for the first time. 

It helped a lot in regards of my photography, especially the part where it forces you to observe things around you. 

When you take the time to breathe and soaking everything in, you start to see things that you might have missed in everyday life.
